in the hill that never existed.

626
01:10:53,800 --> 01:10:56,488
And inside he was waiting for her.

627
01:10:56,584 --> 01:10:58,408
He?

628
01:11:00,616 --> 01:11:03,880
Every night for three months
she went to him.

629
01:11:05,608 --> 01:11:09,256
Then the last night
of the third month,

630
01:11:09,352 --> 01:11:13,000
