631
01:11:13,096 --> 01:11:16,232
- and she was to name the child--
- Beowulf.

632
01:11:18,056 --> 01:11:20,072
Who was he?

633
01:11:21,128 --> 01:11:23,912
My mother died never knowing.

634
01:11:24,008 --> 01:11:26,504
But the Elders had no doubts.

635
01:11:27,752 --> 01:11:30,056
